              Voluptatibus autem at quam ad! Quod itaque totam illo nostrum repellat consequatur beatae rem deserunt
              quisquam nihil! Dolores fugit iure suscipit dignissimos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <a class="dashboard__add-note" href="#">
        <img src="/img/add-icon.png" alt="Add note icon" class="dashboard__add-icon">
        <h2 class="dashboard__add-text">New note</h2>
      </a>
    </div>

    <a class="dashboard__add-column" href="#">
      <img src="/img/add-icon.png" alt="Add note icon" class="dashboard__add-icon">
      <h2 class="dashboard__add-text">New column</h2>
    </a>

  </div>




</body>

</html>